t_area": {"text": "在油烟机市场，消费者对于油烟机的吸力大小与其清洁效果的追求从未停止。近期，美的推出的升级版「蒸汽洗」油烟机，以其独特的清洁方式受到了广泛关注。这种油烟机在做到吸力大且持久的同时，可以通过喷射高温蒸汽来分解和去除油污，相较于传统的人工清洗方式，更为便捷和高效，使用户每天都能用上干净如新的油烟机。但面对这个全新的清洁方式，人们可能会产生疑虑：这种方式的清洁效果如何？它是否会对油烟机造成损害？相比传统的人工清洗，它的用电成本及吸除油烟的能力又是如何？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-3cc427428100f4d8e620c6b5a3e27c04_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "65 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/646556993"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIg72G35SRh/UbEAMaCTEwNTk1NzAwMyCC1YSvBjAAOJsJQAZyCTY0NjU1Njk5M3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "7_1712514045.395240", "card_id": "Q_361253376", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 823}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "法学生到底有多硬核？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "看到问题医学生到底多硬核下的回答挺有趣的，忍不住提问，法学生到底多硬核呢？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-1ac6aab1998f8167e0caac2fb62321dc_720w.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "64 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/361253376"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIg72G35SRh/UbEAMaCDQyNTU2OTI4IO2b3O8FMAA41tEBQAdyCTM2MTI1MzM3NngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "8_1712514045.395498", "card_id": "Q_647292502", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 12}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "在古代做大户人家的庶女 / 